    "note": "MTS and M2TS are structurally identical 192-byte MPEG-TS formats. 'MTS' is the AVCHD camcorder convention; 'M2TS' is the Blu-ray disc convention. Both use the same 4-byte ATS prefix + 188-byte TS packet structure."
  },
